orld championships\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1579}, {\"ngram\": \"the now-banned former governing body\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1657}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic boxing\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1675}, {\"ngram\": \"eligibility tests\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's competition\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both had competed in IBA events for several years without problems, and the Russian-dominated body - which has faced years of clashes with the IOC over judging scandals, leadership decisions and financial issues - has refused to provide any information about the tests, underscoring its lack of transparency in nearly every aspect of its dealings, particularly in recent years.\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9933433960642394, \"rank\": 0.0067002532275058585, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.578204319444643e-32, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several years\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"problems\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"the Russian-dominated body\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 1876, \"to\": 1881}, {\"ngram\": \"clashes\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"scandals\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"leadership decisions\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1949}, {\"ngram\": \"financial issues\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1970}, {\"ngram\": \"any information\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"the tests\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2027}, {\"ngram\": \"its lack\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2050}, {\"ngram\": \"transparency\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly every aspect\", \"from\": 2070, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"its dealings\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us be very clear here: We are talking about women's boxing,\\\" Bach said Saturday.\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2204, \"end\": 2208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999997512532, \"rank\": 2.487484024743093e-10, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2143, \"to\": 2145}, {\"ngram\": \"women's boxing\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2201}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have two boxers who are born as a woman, who have been raised a woman, who have a passport as a woman, and who have competed for many years as women.\", \"from\": 2224, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two boxers\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"a passport\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And this is the clear definition of a woman.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clear definition\", \"from\": 2390, \"to\": 2410}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was never any doubt about them being a woman.\\\"\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2475, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any doubt\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA, which received the unprecedented punishment of being banned from Olympic participation in 2019 following years of conflict with the IOC, disqualified Khelif last year for what it said were elevated levels of testosterone.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2481, \"end\": 2484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9933433960642394, \"rank\": 0.0067002532275058585, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 2618, \"end\": 2621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.578204319444643e-32, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the unprecedented punishment\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic participation\", \"from\": 2551, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"conflict\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"elevated levels\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2690}, {\"ngram\": \"testosterone\", \"from\": 2694, \"to\": 2706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA, which is led by an acquaintance of Russian President Vladimir Putin, has not released more details on the tests, calling 